snippet: Dallas Seavey won the Iditarod for the third time in four years, crossing the finish line in Nome, Alaska, in 8 days 8 hours 13 minutes 6 seconds.
abstract: Dallas Seavey wins Iditarod Trail Dog Sled Race for the third time in four years; his father Mitch Seavey finishes second.
lead_paragraph: Dallas Seavey won the Iditarod for the third time in four years, crossing the finish line in Nome, Alaska, in 8 days 8 hours 13 minutes 6 seconds.

headline.main: Son Tops Father to Claim Iditarod
